ave any questions or comments, please feel free to <strong>contact us 24 hours a day</strong>. We look forward to hearing from you soon. We welcome the opportunity to talk with you and to discuss how we may be of service.\r\n\r\nWhen you enter the office of an attorney, you should feel a welcome and friendly atmosphere, not a stuffy and intimidating environment. At Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, we ensure that our clients first experiences are positive. Long-lasting working relationships have resulted.\r\n\r\nThe lawyers at our firm focus on personalized service and accessibility to our clients. We listen, answer questions and respond to any and all concerns related to a personal injury, family law, or business and family immigration legal matters.\r\n<h3>Advocates for Men and Women in Family Law Matters</h3>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we recognize not only the emotional issues involved in a divorce case, but also the challenges that divorcing men and fathers face. Perceptions abound that a mother can provide a more nurturing environment and attend to all the childrens needs. That is not true in all cases. Our job is to advocate for all clients even when the odds are against them in child custody and child support cases.\r\n<h3>Holding Negligent Individuals, Doctors and Police Officers Accountable</h3>\r\nSuffering a serious injury or losing a loved one due to negligence is a life-changing event that may warrant a lawsuit for compensation. The negligent party should compensate you for your inability to work, pain and suffering, and long-term emotional and physical damages. We provide aggressive and compassionate representation for clients hurt in motor vehicle accidents or victimized by medical malpractice or police brutality.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nTo get more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced personal injury, family law or immigration lawyer, please contact us. If we can\'t help you we will refer you to a competent attorney who can help.', 'Home', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2014-03-10 10:47:13', '2014-03-10 10:47:13', '', '0', 'http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=29', '0', 'page', '', '0');
