 (IRS) in Washington, D.C., Tax Law Specialist</li>\r\n	<li>United States Attorney\'s Office in Washington, D.C., Special Assistant United States Attorney</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Chukwuma I Odelugo', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '801-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-28 05:30:21', '2014-02-28 05:30:21', '', '801', 'http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/801-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
