INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('825', '1', '2014-02-28 06:10:37', '2014-02-28 06:10:37', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Montgomery County Child Custody and Divorce Attorneys</h2>\r\nA dispute over child custody can be rife with emotion. Whether your divorce is taking place in Maryland or Washington, D.C., the best interest of the children must be paramount.\r\n\r\nChild custody is a vital component in resolving a divorce. We strive to utilize the mediation process to find a satisfactory arrangement<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-824\" alt=\"i-prac-childcustody\" src=\"http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/i-prac-childcustody.jpg\" width=\"193\" height=\"253\" /> for both sides, with the best interests of the children in mind.\r\n<h3>Defending Both Fathers\' and Mothers\' Rights in Child Custody Cases</h3>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we defend and protect the rights of our clients involved in child custody disputes. The rights of the father are often forgotten in child custody matters. The mother is often presumed to be the better option for primary or sole custody. Today, fathers are taking a more active role in their children\'s lives and can be as good a parent as, and sometimes better than, the mother.\r\n<h3>Differences in Child Custody Laws in Maryland and Washington, D.C.</h3>\r\nIn Maryland, a presumption of joint custody exists regardless of gender, meaning parents gets equal time with the children. However, men have to provide more proof that they can care for children during their \"tender years.\" That includes providing an adequate residence, working a job schedule conducive to spending time with their children, and being active in all aspects of their child\'s life. Washington, D.C., has no such requirements and shared custody can be as low as 35 percent of the time.\r\n<h3>Focusing on the Best Interests of the Children</h3>\r\nChild custody battles sometimes erupt due to money issues. The more custody responsibility a spouse has, the less paid in child support. At our firm, we believe that parenting time is too vital to modify it over money.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince Georges Plaza. We are near Prince Georges Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nTo get more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced lawyer regarding child visitation, joint custody, legal custody, paternity and fathers\' rights, please contact us.', 'Child Custody', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '823-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-28 06:10:37', '2014-02-28 06:10:37', '', '823', 'http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/823-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('826', '1', '2014-02-28 06:12:51', '2014-02-28 06:12:51', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Maryland Child Support and Support Modification Lawyers</h2>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, we assist with the process of determining child support based on what we hope to be accurate financial data. All the while, your children\'s best interests remains a top priority.<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-827\" alt=\"i-prac-childsupport\" src=\"http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/i-prac-childsupport.jpg\" width=\"193\" height=\"253\" />\r\n\r\nChild support and child custody are sometimes and sadly interwoven together, making time with your children a matter of how much money you will pay or receive. We encourage our clients to avoid any insincere and ultimately damaging battle.\r\n<h3>Child Custody Determining Child Support Amounts</h3>\r\nChild custody plays an important role in determining child support when it is not used for leverage in calculating the final amount. A parent awarded sole custody will obviously receive more money. Shared custody will reduce the amount of child support, while joint physical custody provides no opportunity for child support.\r\n<h3>The Child Support Calculator</h3>\r\nThe child support calculator factors in net income of both spouses, with credits for expenses related to health insurance and daycare. Children from another relationship or marriage are also counted in when determining support amounts.\r\n<h3>Ensuring Accuracy of Data in Child Support Amounts</h3>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we facilitate the difficult and sometimes emotional elements of determining child support. While the final number is based on calculations, the data entered in must be accurate. Spouses engaged in hiding assets or finances to reduce support amounts can be held accountable if money has been concealed from the other spouse.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince Georges Plaza. We are near Prince Georges Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nTo schedule an appointment with an experienced attorney regarding child support guidelines, support modifications or the need to establish paternity, please contact us.', 'Child Support', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'child-support', '', '', '2014-03-10 10:47:13', '2014-03-10 10:47:13', '', '0', 'http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=826', '0', 'page', '', '0');
