INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('832', '1', '2014-02-28 06:17:59', '2014-02-28 06:17:59', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Hyattsville, Maryland, Immigration and Naturalization Attorneys</h2>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, we help overseas clients enter the United States for purposes of contributing to the workforce. Our firm also assists with family immigration matters as well.<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-833\" alt=\"i-prac-businessfamilyvisas\" src=\"http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/i-prac-businessfamilyvisas.jpg\" width=\"193\" height=\"253\" />\r\n\r\nWhether your job involves a specialty, low skills or no skills, you can apply for a visa. The immigration process may be lengthy, depending on your profession, but we will advocate for you throughout the entire process.\r\n<h3>Challenges in Changing Status With Business Visas</h3>\r\nDoctors, nurses, athletes, entertainers or persons in any job that has a high demand face reduced processing time in securing a business visa. Those types of visas also allow the individual to apply for an adjustment in status. H1-B visas are not of the type whose status can be adjusted.\r\n<h3>Knowledge of Immigration Law and Procedures</h3>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we maintain a thorough knowledge of the laws and regulations established by the Bureau of United States Citizenship and Immigration Services (USCIS). Information is vital when a client comes to our office seeking an answer to an immigration-related inquiry or help securing a visa, especially when they are seeking permanent residency for a spouse or close family member. Whether you are trying to secure a business visa or permanent residency for a family member, we will help facilitate the process and advocate for you until your immigration case is resolved.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince Georges Plaza. We are near Prince Georges Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nTo get more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced family immigration or business immigration lawyer regarding citizenship, a fianc visa or a work visa, please contact us.', 'Business Family Visas', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'business-family-visas', '', '', '2014-03-10 10:47:13', '2014-03-10 10:47:13', '', '0', 'http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=832', '0', 'page', '', '0');
