d personal injury and medical malpractice clients from all areas in DC and MD.\r\n\r\nMr. Odelugo also defended individuals charged with all types of crimes, including felonies and misdemeanors. Mr. Odelugo has represented those charged with crimes from murder to shoplifting, from embezzlement to assault, from drunk driving to drug offenses, and nearly every other crime imaginable.\r\n\r\nMr. Odelugo brings 18 years of aggressive representation, and he takes pride and great satisfaction in assisting our firm in fighting for our clients. Mr. Odelugo is proud of what our firm has accomplished for our clients.\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Areas of Practice</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Personal Injury</li>\r\n	<li>Automobile Accidents</li>\r\n	<li>Medical Malpractice</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Bar Admissions</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>District of Columbia, 1990</li>\r\n	<li>Maryland</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Education</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>American University, Washington College of Law, Washington, District of Columbia</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>J.D.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Law Journal: Washington College of Law Administrative Law Journal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Southern University in Louisiana</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor\'s Degree</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Major: History</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong>University of Maryland</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor\'s Degree</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Major: Accounting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Past Employment Positions</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hon. John Garret Penn, Former Chief Judge United States District Court for the District of Columbia, Judicial Intern</li>\r\n	<li>District of Columbia Department of Finance and Revenue, Attorney-Advisor</li>\r\n	<li>Employee Pension and Exempt Organizations Division for the Internal Revenue Service (IRS) in Washington, D.C., Tax Law Specialist</li>\r\n	<li>United States Attorney\'s Office in Washington, D.C., Special Assistant United States Attorney</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Chukwuma I. Odelugo', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '801-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-05 08:59:10', '2014-03-05 08:59:10', '', '801', 'http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/801-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1057', '1', '2014-03-05 09:02:03', '2014-03-05 09:02:03', '<strong><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-783\" alt=\"Anitha Johnson\" src=\"http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/attorney_img1.png\" width=\"213\" height=\"238\" />Managing Partner</strong>\r\nLocation: Lanham, Maryland\r\nPhone: [number type=\"1\"]\r\n\r\nAnitha Johnson started working for ODELUGO &amp; ASSOCIATES, PLLC in 1999. Ms. Johnson is very compassionate, and she takes all her clients\' concerns personally. Ms. Johnson is a dedicated trial attorney who handles Personal Injury Matters, Family Law Matters, and Immigration Matters, among other matters.\r\n\r\nAfter graduating from Baltimore Polytechnic Institute, Ms. Johnson attended and graduated from the University of Maryland in College Park, Maryland, and she ended her education at the University of Baltimore School of Law.\r\n\r\nMs. Johnson started working for ODELUGO &amp; ASSOCIATES, PLLC, in 1999. In 2005, due to her hard work and success, Ms. Johnson became the managing partner of the firm, and the firm changed its name to ODELUGO &amp; JOHNSON, LLC. Ms. Johnson is licensed to practice law in all the Courts in the State of Maryland, and in the Courts in Washington, D.C. Ms. Johnson is an active member of DC Trial Lawyers, Maryland Trial Lawyers, and American Immigration Lawyers Associations.\r\n\r\nMs. Johnson has had great success advocating for her clients. She has obtain millions in settlements and jury verdicts for her clients and has had many successful criminal verdicts. Ms. Johnson\'s clients enjoys her down-to-earth personality, her persistence in obtaining her clients\' objectives, and her extensive trial advocacy skills. Ms. Johnson believes that her success comes from her ability to enjoy her work, care about her clients\' needs, and determination in achieving the best outcome for her clients.\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Areas of Practice</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Immigration and Naturalization</li>\r\n	<li>Family Law</li>\r\n	<li>Personal Injury</li>\r\n	<li>Medical Malpractice</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Bar Admissions</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Maryland, 2005</li>\r\n	<li>District of Columbia, 2006</li>\r\n	<li>U.S. District Court District of Maryland</li>\r\n	<li>U.S. District Court of the District of Columbia</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Education</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>University of Baltimore School of Law, Baltimore, Maryland</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>J.D. - 2005</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Baltimore Polytechnic Institute</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>University of Maryland, College Park, Maryland</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>B.A. - 1999</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Professional Associations and Memberships</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Maryland State Bar Association, Member</li>\r\n	<li>The District of Columbia Bar, Member</li>\r\n	<li>District of Columbia Trial Lawyers Association, Member</li>\r\n	<li>Maryland Trial Lawyers Association, Member</li>\r\n	<li>American Immigration Lawyers Association, Member</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"vcard\" style=\"display: none;\"><span class=\"fn\">Anitha W. Johnson</span><br />\r\n  <span class=\"org\">Odelugo & Johnson, LLC</span><br />\r\n  <a class=\"email\"href=\"mailto:\"Anitha.Johnson@odelugojohnson.com \">\"Anitha.Johnson@odelugojohnson.com \"</a><br />\r\n  <span class=\"note\">Attorney</span><br />\r\n  <span class=\"adr\"><br />\r\n  <span class=\"street-address\">4601 Presidents Drive, Suite 145</span><br />\r\n  <span class=\"locality\">Lanham</span>,<br />\r\n  <abbr class=\"region\" title=\"Maryland\">MD</abbr><br />\r\n  <span class=\"postal-code\">20706</span><br />\r\n  <span class=\"country-name\">USA</span><br />\r\n  <span class=\"tel\">(410) 870-7323</span><br />\r\n  <a class=\"url\" \"http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/\">www.odelugojohnsonllc.com</a></span></div>', 'Anitha W. Johnson', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '797-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-05 09:02:03', '2014-03-05 09:02:03', '', '797', 'http://benjamingkelson.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/797-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
